WEBVTT

00:01.802 --> 00:02.812
- Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.836 --> 00:04.238
We are not free.

00:04.272 --> 00:06.074
Even when they unlock
the door to this prison,

00:06.107 --> 00:07.408
we are still prisoners.

00:07.441 --> 00:08.676
- Is it okay if I listen?

00:08.709 --> 00:10.144
- What's your book
got to say about

00:10.178 --> 00:11.612
what's happening in America?

00:11.645 --> 00:14.215
- I'm in here because
I stood up for people.

00:14.248 --> 00:15.516
Outside of our Movement.

00:15.549 --> 00:17.351
People whose water
was being poisoned.

00:17.385 --> 00:18.686
- Oh, I'm so glad you're here.

00:18.719 --> 00:20.421
Can you look at my baby?

00:20.454 --> 00:22.623
- Go back to the van and get her
some more water, okay?

00:22.656 --> 00:25.593
- I love our life,
I love this house.

00:25.626 --> 00:27.428
But we can have more.

00:27.461 --> 00:29.563
- Now that I'm becoming
a father, I have needs

00:29.597 --> 00:31.765
for my individual family.

00:31.799 --> 00:32.700
- Like?

00:32.732 --> 00:34.435
- A new refrigerator
for the guest house.

00:34.468 --> 00:35.736
- I am so sorry, Eddie.

00:41.842 --> 00:43.844
The stuff that Dekaan
puts in that water

00:43.877 --> 00:45.579
isn't gonna show up
on your average tests.

00:45.613 --> 00:46.780
- Can you find it?
- Yeah.

00:46.814 --> 00:48.316
But it's not cheap.

00:48.349 --> 00:50.151
Libby Dekaan
had my son arrested.

00:50.184 --> 00:52.520
I have to pull the funding
for the water testing.

00:52.553 --> 00:54.222
- Don't need to have
the water tested.

00:54.255 --> 00:56.657
I know what's in
the fuckin' water.

00:56.690 --> 00:58.126
That's not what
blood looks like.

00:58.159 --> 01:00.060
That's poison.

